The paper discusses the use of compressive sensing for video data, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) research. The paper also mentions optimization techniques, which fall under information theory (cs.IT). The use of sparsity and incoherence in compressive sensing is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE).
